["addation_3e0c7cfb6d7f44a0"] = "Now that we have our fill of suntans and Tequila Sunrises, it\'s time to start planning for something juicy again. I got something in mind, but to set it up, we need some help, and the help I have in mind will take some convincing. So we gotta do something to impress them. I\'ve got a couple sweet options for you to pick from...", 
