["addation_03bb93d4687ceafd"] = "Looks like The Butcher\'s burgeoning international operations hit something of a snag. The Sosa cartel have been interfering with her shipments. We made a little Balkan friend. Let\'s keep her that way.", 
["addation_70b832a79ca048a4"] = "Complete the Diamond Store job.$NL;This assignment requires you to play from the lobby to the end of the heist.", 
