["addation_1f851c99db5751a8"] = "This game saves data automatically at certain points.$NL;Please don\'t turn off your Xbox One when the following icon is displayed:", 
["addation_2e07a6e72079e9bd"] = "You have already joined this room.", 
["addation_d89875aec8c4203a"] = "Great work. Left those Murkywater goons scratching their asses and wondering where their shit went. Gage is happy, and Murkywater isn\'t. This means you\'re starting to get notorious. And, at the end of the day, notoriety is your life-blood. Money can be stolen, see. Gold can come and go. But notoriety - that\'s what you\'re really worth. So let\'s get some more.", 
["addation_4ed68dbb4f27f604"] = "The game you have been invited to is running another version of PAYDAY 2. You are unable to join.", 
["addation_0efe6bca213238fc"] = "(Your removed modifications will be placed in the inventory)", 
["addation_28b144a0be27ae6c"] = "Friends, I promise I will see you to the end of this, yeah? Bain has been secretly searching for some kind of Holy Grail Dinges for along time and I am committed to help. He may be gone, but the search will continue. Duke has managed to start uncovering a lot of new leads on it, digging through volumes of ancient lore. Before he got taken, Bain set up a plan to find an artifact buried in the foundation of a bank in Brooklyn. This artifact was put there in the early 1900s and may contain clues we need.", 
["addation_f9a95f51cad74aa0"] = "Complete either The Bomb: Dockyard or The Bomb: Forest jobs  on the Very Hard difficulty or higher.$NL;This assignment requires you to play from the lobby to the end of the heist.", 
["addation_dac575ce2b781a59"] = "In order to save, you must be signed into a profile. Do you want to sign in now?", 
["addation_e3fab6edb7907bec"] = "Connection to the host has been lost", 
["addation_c7b25e6e5fe83069"] = "Progress file wrong version. Version $VERSION; or higher is required. Try loading again?", 
["addation_adf1dac23b488fe2"] = "Paying Rent", 
["addation_16516e46052df69e"] = "Playing multiplayer heist", 
["addation_9ba29179715f2a76"] = "You proved you have what it takes to get in, get loud and get the job done. That brings contacts our way. Here\'s our first - Vlad Kozak. Vlad\'s crazy. Even for someone spat from the Russian mobscene, this big guy stands apart, Well, he likes your work. We\'ll see if that\'s a good thing. But before he lets you into bed with him, you\'re going to have to do a little grunt work.", 
["addation_6651de972f808567"] = "A sign-in change occurred.$NL;You have been returned to the Title screen.", 
["addation_1a909df13ba3a2b3"] = "Sign-in change", 
["addation_42124e2d44f483dd"] = "You don\'t have what it takes yet. To become infamous, you will need to get to reputation level $level; and pay a fee of $cash; from your offshore account along with your skill points and the rest of your spending cash.", 
["addation_e520ef16710d7e7e"] = "Waiting for game to respond", 
["addation_bea985edfb6ebfa6"] = "Progress file wrong version. Data will now be deleted.", 
["addation_f3daf9db4056fa2b"] = "Are you sure you would like to terminate the current contract?$NL;$NL;You and your crew will be returned to the planning phase where a new contract can be selected.", 
["addation_622c3f8d9cb14f87"] = "YOU HAVE A NEW MESSAGE", 
["addation_52f6b003c37edb41"] = "Singleplayer heist ended", 
["addation_05381aa055d2829d"] = "Your Crime Spree has failed due to an unexpected closure of the game.$NL;You can still pay the Continental Coin cost to continue.", 
["addation_404ca5dfb61a5180"] = "TRANSACTION SUCCESSFUL", 
["addation_d3cc35a78a39cca2"] = "Visit your safehouse atleast once.", 
["addation_26846c65cbc7a942"] = "Polar Safari", 
["addation_105ad4284504bc4b"] = "Vlad\'s happy, and, trust me, we want to keep that guy smiling. He\'s so happy, in fact, he\'s got a couple of jobs for you that\'re a little bit personal. Do these for him, he says, and we\'re gonna be his top guys. Can\'t hurt to do the big guy a couple of little favors, can it?", 
["addation_1db93cb94b0fccf7"] = "Killing The Commissar means The Dentist can get to the DA. And that opens things up for us in the field of maximum security prison transfers. Of course, there\'s only one guy inside that we care about - our old friend Hoxton. He\'s a high-value, maximum security prisoner for the Feds. Putting pressure on the DA means we can get Hoxton into position for a break-out. So that\'s exactly what we\'re going to do.", 
["addation_9178575fd5be4d60"] = "If you sell this, you will be paid $money;.", 
["addation_1abef1248ad3f974"] = "Complete the Alaskan Deal job on the Very Hard difficulty or higher.$NL;This assignment requires you to play from the lobby to the end of the heist.", 
["addation_060a89ae41c94ac2"] = "Complete the Scarface job on the Very Hard difficulty or higher.$NL;This assignment requires you to play from the lobby to the end of the heist.", 
