["addation_3f091d09a1f40520"] = "Repair", 
["addation_c797457e91f657d3"] = "Reach reputation level 25.", 
["addation_35b5c016204be3aa"] = "I\'ve been trying to find more ways to cash in on Murkywater. They have tentacles spread all over the place, and have an uncanny way of turning up where you least expect it. There\'s definitely more to them than what we\'ve seen. They\'ve got a supply line running through D.C. I\'ve been looking at, and it finally looks like something worth our while is coming through.", 
["addation_7a1de103c7360ccf"] = "PAYDAY 2", 
["addation_d74b5123f3895832"] = "The New York Situation", 
["addation_116e79d6a55057d4"] = "Kicked out", 
["addation_a72472ec93e515de"] = "All right, we got a new contact. A politician, calling himself The Elephant. Job is a bit of industrial sabotage. Some hot-shot scientist has figured out cold fusion. Sort of technology that will make the oil companies as dead as disco. And the "Powers That Be" have a lot of money in those companies, so The Elephant and his friends want to make sure this technology gets buried. Fine by me.", 
