["addation_07a362cc844b7c2f"] = "Animal Farm", 
["addation_86b59652c69a9a8e"] = "Hector\'s got a plan for finishing off the Mendozas, who we reckon are being moved out of the country. Part of that plan is getting info off another gang, the Cobras, but they don\'t want money - they want meth. Hector won\'t use his own people for this, so we\'re going to see the deal goes down. This could be what puts Hector top of the pile, so it\'s worth our time.", 
