["addation_468ab5ba85d8fd53"] = "You\'ve come a long way, but don\'t think for a moment that this is the end. It isn\'t. You\'ve made the Payday Gang the most wanted gang in the land. Keep it up. Get out there. Rob some banks. Pull off some heists. Do what you do best.", 
