["addation_59228675f11dd568"] = "Hector, that rat, is in the ground. Now, The Dentist is setting us after something special. He\'s not saying what it is just yet. First things first, though. There\'s a Diamond at the McKendrick Museum - THE Diamond. It\'s a valuable rock, and we\'re after it. The Dentist needs this diamond for something big, really big and we want a piece of it, so lets get get over to the Museum and grab that stone.", 
