["addation_0d74d92dfc93dd2a"] = "Are you sure you want to leave this lobby?", 
["addation_5063e4875ab8a5e8"] = "Looks like Locke took us for a bunch of chumps in Alaska and the Butcher is pissed. After what he pulled, we need to show him what happens when you mess with us. Locke has gone dark for the moment, but he\'s got investments in the Garnet group. If we put a big dent in their finances, it\'s gonna hurt Locke too, so I\'ve got a little job for you that\'ll do just that.", 
["addation_9153cb24a0f7b863"] = "Payment Due", 
["addation_a79a4a695c4f4a0d"] = "Complete the Big Bank job on the Very Hard difficulty or higher.$NL;This assignment requires you to play from the lobby to the end of the heist.", 
["addation_bef614eff422e8bb"] = "Pieces Off The Board", 
["addation_bceda1db1fc92ef1"] = "Complete The Diamond job on the Very Hard difficulty or higher.$NL;This assignment requires you to play from the lobby to the end of the heist.", 
["addation_31550cca23c639e7"] = "This room no longer exists, please try another one.", 
["addation_768a5fc39f319b9d"] = "Your mask has not been finalized. Aborting will leave the mask unchanged.", 
["addation_6a583287fe2a8608"] = "Not signed in", 
["addation_11ee08039efe03da"] = "In the safe house", 
["addation_5b75662e329d60a2"] = "I don\'t like it when people are trying to force our hands but this guy, The Dentist, has the means to get our associate back. If we want to be able to break Hoxton out of prison we have to play along with The Dentist\'s little plans. Although "little" is truly the wrong word here. The first job he "so kindly" asks us to do might be the biggest job we\'ve done yet. He wants us to prove ourselves with the ultimate bank heist - the Benevolent Bank. It\'s never been successfully hit. If we pull this off, he says he\'ll help us get a chance to get Hoxton back. But not for free, I guess we\'ll hear more from him after the job.", 
["addation_eb4a6c0cfb1c060d"] = "Gain 20 Crime Spree levels.", 
["addation_353075d7a4fd431c"] = "Yeah... it feels like everyone is asking for help from the Payday Gang now. Vlad wants us to help out his cousin, who somehow got wind of our adventure in the Motherland. He\'s been good for us so far, so if you\'re up for it, why not hear what he has to say? Or if you\'re in the mood for something more... greasy, he also mentioned a warehouse full of bikers that need to be shown the way to some holiday cheer. Up to you, guys.", 
["addation_8fd151d8aa33c0ea"] = "You can only purchase one Gage Boost per Crime Spree mission.", 
["addation_fa8709891343c7eb"] = "Complete The Biker Heist on the Very Hard difficulty or higher.$NL;This assignment requires you to play from the lobby to the end of the heist.", 
