["addation_76e15a203eb12454"] = "YOU MUST BE ONLINE TO MAKE USE OF NETWORK MODES.", 
["addation_4eb87f6f86513dc4"] = "Complete the Heat Street job on the Very Hard difficulty or higher.$NL;This assignment requires you to play from the lobby to the end of the heist.", 
["addation_b39b3a21eeb99c63"] = "Steam could not authenticate Steam ID for the host.", 
["addation_52961383d8fddf2b"] = "CHAT IS DISABLED ON YOUR Sony Entertainment Network Account DUE TO PARENTAL CONTROL RESTRICTIONS.", 
["addation_37bbdc4b4784cb36"] = "Welcome to the demo of PAYDAY 2!", 
["addation_98a18512ea6d867b"] = "Gang, after a little not-so-friendly persuasion, we got us a lead on Kento. A guy by the name of Kazuo supposedly has some info for us, with one little snag; he\'s rattling bars at D.C. Central. Lucky for you, I\'ve arranged a transfer, so all we gotta do is make sure to grab him when it happens. This one is gonna get really loud, and I don\'t think we\'ll be too popular with the D.D.O.T. afterward, \'cause they\'re gonna be fixing more than potholes- we\'re taking down a bridge!", 
