["addation_77172d923d401ff0"] = "Before we begin, we gotta wipe your slate clean. That means erasing whatever dirt the Feds already got on you. You\'re nothing to them right now, so this shouldn\'t be too hard. Don\'t worry, I got your back and will talk you through it. Gives me a chance to make sure you\'re still up for this life.", 
